<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: assembly_bond_definition
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition">
<p>

An <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/>
that defines a joint that uses material to bond together portions
of the assembly.  An <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_bond_definition"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR1">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall have exactly one  <express_ref linkend="material_property_definition_schema:ir_express:material_property_definition_schema.material_designation"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR2">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be in exactly one <express_ref linkend="External_item_identification_assignment:mim:External_item_identification_assignment_mim.applied_external_identification_assignment"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR3">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as the 'bonded feature 1'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR4
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR4">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as the 'bonded feature 2'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR5
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR5">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be an aspect of the shape of an <express_ref linkend="product_identification_extension:mim:Product_identification_extension_mim.externally_defined_product_definition"/> for a product in the 'technology specific model' category.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_bond_definition.WR6
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.wr:WR6">
The <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be an aspect of the shape of an <express_ref linkend="product_identification_extension:mim:Product_identification_extension_mim.externally_defined_product_definition"/> with a name of 'assembly bond model' product.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: assembly_bond_definition.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition.ur:UR1">
The name of the <b>assembly_bond_definition</b> shall be unique.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: assembly_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint"><p>
An <b>assembly_joint</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> and
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> that is the result of a physical connection between two
components in the assembly.  The order shall be inferred from the
use of relating and related attributes on  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.
An <b>assembly_joint</b> implements the ARM
concepts of:
</p><ul>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_joint"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembled_with_bonding"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembled_with_fasteners"/>.</li>
</ul>

</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR1">
The <b>assembly_joint</b> shall have a <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> that references
either a  <express_ref linkend="Component_feature:mim:Component_feature_mim.component_terminal"/> with a description of 'assembly module component
terminal', 'bare die component terminal', 'interconnect component join
terminal', 'interconnect module component terminal', 
'package terminal occurrence', or  'packaged component join terminal', or a
 <express_ref linkend="Interface_component:mim:Interface_component_mim.physical_component_interface_terminal"/> or a  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_design:mim:Assembly_module_design_mim.component_mounting_feature"/> or an
 <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_with_interconnect_component:mim:Assembly_module_with_interconnect_component_mim.interconnect_module_component_surface_feature"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR2">
The <b>assembly_joint</b> shall have a <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> that references
either a  <express_ref linkend="Component_feature:mim:Component_feature_mim.component_terminal"/> with a description of 'assembly module component
terminal', 'bare die component terminal', 'interconnect component join
terminal', 'interconnect module component terminal', 
'package terminal occurrence', or  'packaged component join terminal', or a
 <express_ref linkend="Interface_component:mim:Interface_component_mim.physical_component_interface_terminal"/> or a  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_design:mim:Assembly_module_design_mim.component_mounting_feature"/> or an
 <express_ref linkend="Assembly_module_with_interconnect_component:mim:Assembly_module_with_interconnect_component_mim.interconnect_module_component_surface_feature"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR3">
If the name of the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> of the <b>assembly_joint</b> is
'assembled with bonding', it shall be related to exactly one  
 <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:mim:Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition"/> as the 'default definition usage'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR4
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR4">
If the name of the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> of the <b>assembly_joint</b> is
'assembled with bonding', it shall have at most one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.property_definition"/> that
is associated with exactly one representation with a name of 'bond assembly
position' that contains exactly one  <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> with the name 'assembly
position'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR5
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR5">
If the name of the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> of the <b>assembly_joint</b> is 
'assembled with fasteners', it shall be an aspect of the shape of an  <express_ref linkend="Component_grouping:mim:Component_grouping_mim.assembly_group_component_definition"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR6
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR6">
The <b>assembly_joint</b> is shall be an aspect of the shape of a  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:mim:Physical_unit_usage_view_mim.physical_unit"/> that is an assembly module design or of an  <express_ref linkend="Component_grouping:mim:Component_grouping_mim.assembly_group_component_definition"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR7
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR7">
If the name of the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> of the <b>assembly_joint</b> is 'assembled with bonding', its bonded features shall be defined by the referenced features.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: assembly_joint.WR8
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint.wr:WR8">
The members of <b>assembly_joint</b> shall form a directed acyclic graph with the <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/>, <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> attributes of <b>assembly_joint</b>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: component_mating_constraint_condition
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.component_mating_constraint_condition">
<p>

A <b>component_mating_constraint_condition</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> that implements the ARM
concept of  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Component_mating_constraint_condition"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: component_mating_constraint_condition.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.component_mating_constraint_condition.ur:UR1">
The name shall be unique within the context of the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.product_definition_shape"/> referenced as <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect.of_shape"/> inherited from the  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> supertype.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: connection_zone_based_assembly_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.connection_zone_based_assembly_joint">
<p>

A <b>connection_zone_based_assembly_joint</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:mim:Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_joint"/> that includes the
identification of the connection zones that are to be mated in addition to the specific
features that are to be mated.  A <b>connection_zone_based_assembly_joint</b> implements the ARM
concept of <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Connection_zone_based_assembly_joint"/>.

</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.wr:WR1">
The <b>connection_zone_based_assembly_joint</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as 'zone 1' by
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.<express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/>. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.wr:WR2">
The <b>connection_zone_based_assembly_joint</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as 'zone 2' by
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.<express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.connection_zone_based_assembly_joint.wr:WR3">
The <b>connection_zone_based_assembly_joint</b> shall be related to only <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect">shape_aspects</express_ref> with a description of 'connection zone'. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation">
A <b>reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_usage_view:mim:Physical_unit_usage_view_mim.physical_unit"/>.  A <b>reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation</b> implements the ARM concept of a <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation.wr:WR1">
The <b>reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation</b> name shall be 'assembly model' and it shall be a definition of a product that is classified as an 'template model'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation.wr:WR2">
If the <b>reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation</b> is a physical design, it shall relate to exactly
one <b>reference_packaged_part_assembly_implementation</b> that is a physical design usage with a 
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> name of 'assembly module' as the design usage.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: default_assembly_bond_shape_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.default_assembly_bond_shape_constraint">
<p>

The <b>default_assembly_bond_shape_constraint</b> rule constrains the usage of
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> when it is used as a default assembly bond shape.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: default_assembly_bond_shape_constraint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Assembly_technology_mim.default_assembly_bond_shape_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each  <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/>\representation.name = 'default assembly bond shape' 
shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:mim:Assembly_technology_mim.assembly_bond_definition"/>.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
